So Hey Guess What? Im not quite sure right now, but what i am sure of is that im bored. So i havent posted in a long time. Well whats new eh?:
*X* me n john are still together, its not new but its not old eh?
*X* I love my pookie bear very muchly!
Well seriously though. . . nothing is very new other than ive had a job for a little while now which i am putting in my two weeks notice soon and finding another job because for one: the management are assholes, two: the co-wrokers are assholes, three: i hate the job, four: its way too fucking hot in there, and most importantly five: they are pricks and not giving me any hours at all so i am making no money pretty much .. and they are ripping me off! .. the part i wont like when i do quit there is that i wont have my gym membership ne more :( which is sad .. but ne ways idk .. nothing is really all that new i guess. . .
Life isnt going very well lately.. idk it just sucks like it used to i guess. . .I just dont know how to enjoy it ne more? Idk . . . i really love my pookie bear, and thats all i know right now. . . it makes me so sad how we fight a lot lately. . . and when he gets super angry or super depressed its always because of me and i hate doing this to him. . . sometimes i feel like i should just leave him be because he would be super happy without me. . .but in reality i could never do that and i could never let him let me go because i love him way to fucking much to just let him go. . . i guess every good relationship starts off with dissagreements at first. . .all i know is i wanna be with him long enough to be in the middle of the dance floor in a big fluffy pretty prom dress with the most handsome boy ever dancing away the night. . . then walking down that pretty white floral aisle to the man i love. . . then all the way to the end of life's journey where ill rest with him forever. I am so in love with him .. i just wish we could stop fighting all the time .. i wish i could just stop being a fuck up...
Ne who im gunna skidattle fer now. . .
